Those arguments will now take place after a committee of customers affected by FTX’s collapse, known as a creditor committee, can be established. A representative for the U.S. government said that forming a committee has been difficult due to the geographical dispersion of the failed company's customers.&nbsp;<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
But Judge Dorsey kept a hearing in the case scheduled for Friday at 10 a.m. EST in case lawyers to hear further arguments around the computer access issue if a resolution can't be reached outside of court.&nbsp;
